727411f-c.text:
Metropolitan Avenue (tracks thereon) at the S.E. corner of Himrod Street, showing two homes in this set of three views belonging to one Hetling. The smaller house perched on the hill was demolished prior to 1934. H.C. Herring was the probable owner
from 1860 to 1873.
1922
Views 1,2 and 3
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
